Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:11.99,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... it's summer break now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.57,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.04,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.78,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:33.01,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.84,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.15,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,it's your humbled brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.24,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first day of summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:44.45,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.77,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.26,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...I can stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:50.74,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...sane at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.54,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.21,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you buy that camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:38.30,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It looks pretty old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It was in our shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.55,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I think it belonged to my \Ngrandfather, who's passed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.64,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I like it for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.72,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,How do you use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.58,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You put in this film,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.98,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and then focus the lens and\Npress the shutter button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.44,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:00.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You're really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.95,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You're already being really \Nfrank with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.90,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,and it's only the first day of break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.02,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.52,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.89,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.67,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kaito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.97,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Stretching, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:25.53,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the fun of \Ncreating our movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.18,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.12,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What are we filming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.35,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.79,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai's the one \Nwriting the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.02,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.11,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I have the script we'll \Nneed for today done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.72,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,The script for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.36,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I write scripts in the Hong Kong-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:43.82,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:48.07,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I figure out what we're going\Nto film the morning of the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just winging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.40,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We're done changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:58.44,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks great on you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.87,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.64,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the cosplay club \Nat school for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.95,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cosplay club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.33,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.43,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.35,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.18,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I-It looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.56,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:25.64,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll be filming the scene where\Nthe heroine first meets the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.01,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.67,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That might be really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:32.32,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the heroine is an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty avant-garde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.61,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's wearing that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.46,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,After arriving on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:42.57,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,the heroine has a fateful \Nencounter with an Earth boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.66,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be ad-libbing all the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.84,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.87,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.73,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And who'll be playing the Earth boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I have to run the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.77,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,So that leaves me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.92,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I think that'd be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.34,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.60,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I was just planning on helping \Nout behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.71,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:05.15,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.76,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You respond based on \Nthe situation at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.37,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,A set is a living creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.38,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You talk like you've \Nbeen on one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.68,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:17.22,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to be in a scene with\Nsomebody as pretty as Takatsuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:20.21,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be an \Nunforgettable memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.55,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,These are supposed to be \Nthe best days of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.83,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.72,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be playing an alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.69,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.23,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.98,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun, I'm all ready here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.44,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.23,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.46,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,a planet in the F stage of \Ndevelopment on the edge of civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,They've just started moving into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.29,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The only place they've managed to reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.58,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...with a manned craft is \Ntheir satellite, the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.49,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty realistic dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.97,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,She's speaking kind \Nof stilted, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:11.00,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigaki-kun needs to enter next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:11.93,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:17.22,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's a reason why\NI came to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.38,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.56,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.47,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.28,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,F-For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.58,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That changes the setting \Nso they've already met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.49,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.48,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you \Nthis whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.41,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You're an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.59,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a Man in Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.70,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,M-Man in Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.04,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.30,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.55,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, \NIchika, Ishigaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.82,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I just got into it all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.27,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The main guy died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You did a really good job ad-libbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.35,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.98,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.97,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Since the movie's story changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.86,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,we're waiting for ideas \Nfrom Remon-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly the heroine starts to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:23.23,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and the Men in Black try \Nto catch her, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.24,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.26,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.07,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lake a little \Nfurther up here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:37.84,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You told me there was a \Nplace you wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.46,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tree there, and a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.91,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really have anything\Nspecial to identify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.27,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That'd make it hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.90,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.06,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd still like to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun, you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.92,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I picked a place similar to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.60,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess this wasn't it. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.91,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:10.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.80,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.26,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, take those drinks over \Nto Ichika-senpai and Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:29.63,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.42,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering for \Na while now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:36.38,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro, do you know how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.48,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.60,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you known?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.25,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.54,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.77,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've been friends \Nsince we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.16,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.70,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,If you find someone, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.96,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.01,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.73,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Kitahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.31,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.98,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of spaced out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.16,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.24,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start filming again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.12,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,In order to escape her pursuers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:22.30,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,the heroine returns to her spaceship\Nand meets up with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.31,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.46,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to play the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:25.99,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,This guy will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.83,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.92,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,When did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:33.05,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be the biological entity that acts\Nas a terminal for the spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.55,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.02,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.55,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.30,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai, we're ready here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.27,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.60,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure who the \Ndirector is anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.39,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Camera, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.78,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.95,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And action.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.03,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,People are after me. Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.31,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.43,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:14.95,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking revenge for my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:19.97,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.64,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:27.24,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, Ichika, \NIshigaki-kun, Rinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.46,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just run in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.23,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's just my actor's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're getting \Na little too into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.78,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so what are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.28,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:43.57,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We sit and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You have no place to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.47,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:53.41,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How about staying at my place, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:57.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I live by myself, and I have extra rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.80,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:10:59.80,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.63,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.04,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.92,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.03,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally gotten into the story now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.11,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.32,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.82,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,When did I become an \Nactor here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.45,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.74,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You get to be who\NIchika-senpai ends up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.45,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you do that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.37,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:32.04,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun's become the \Nlead guy in the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Seems it ended up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.31,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think things are going \Nto play out between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:37.98,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:45.98,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Then what way do you \Nthink it should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.64,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if they could end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.60,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:58.13,Natsu-Ep-Title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5\NSenpai is the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.75,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It would, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:06.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Both the director and camera operator\Nended up being Remon-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for taking a bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.16,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The bath was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So are we filming again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.38,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.00,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on Remon-senpai, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.34,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.93,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai said she wanted me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.61,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...to get as many scenes as \NI could possibly film...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...of the heroine getting used \Nto life here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.40,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to film me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.69,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:39.73,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about the movie here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:45.39,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do if you found\Nout who the heroine really was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:49.08,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai'll be the one \Nto figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.95,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what you \Nwould do personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.96,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I would think it \Nwas pretty amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:01.70,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I would ask her to \Ntake me to space with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's regulations against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.74,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.10,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be okay being with \Nsomeone from another planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.25,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they don't \Nexcrete any weird fluids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.58,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Then sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.31,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't really bug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.44,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.42,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:24.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.36,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.58,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.23,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Tanigawa residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.08,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mio. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.49,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So no filming then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.99,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'd be hard, with this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:44.55,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.38,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.68,Natsu-Italic,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.73,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.73,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.69,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:02.07,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Takatsuki-senpai, have you \Ngotten used to living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.28,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm doing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:06.61,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But Senpai's kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.57,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She made chocolate flavored \Ncurry the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.35,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.00,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.56,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.54,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I need to buy ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.43,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's stop by the grocery \Nstore on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.10,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.50,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,And we're almost out of tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.75,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Detergent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.70,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's stop \Nby the pharmacy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.96,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.00,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.09,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.76,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,My mom told me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.53,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,They're greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.18,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.91,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun, this is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.77,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This house is pretty old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.52,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a look at the \Nroof when it clears up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.51,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:14.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not something \Nthat happens every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.61,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tanigawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.25,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry for walking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not really \Nmy house, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:26.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I know. How about we \Neat lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.16,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.20,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kanna went somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.99,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.63,Natsu-Main,Kanna's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.16,Natsu-Main,Kanna's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She took the greens we had \Nin the house with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.42,Natsu-Main,Kanna's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's my daughter, but \Nshe's pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:52.53,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, when she gets back, \Ntell her I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.61,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.42,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.98,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You made sandwiches out of the greens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.14,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might as well \Nuse them since I got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.80,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.49,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:17.08,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like vegetable dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.95,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I got over that \Ngrapefruit and rice stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.79,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much take on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.79,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You're filming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to film as much as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa, you help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.90,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.36,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Try having a normal \Nconversation together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.02,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A normal conversation might be kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.54,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.60,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san, do you have any siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.24,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an only child,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:01.21,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,but I've played with \NTetsuro since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.08,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,so I was never really lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So you've known Ishigaki-kun \Nfor a long time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.89,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of like a dumb \Nlittle brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.86,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.43,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigaki-kun kind of looks \Nlike an older brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.93,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You just think that because he's tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.77,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.89,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I have an older sister \Nand a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.24,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So three sisters then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.42,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.31,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There are only girls in our house,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.23,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,so coming here was kind of different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.34,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what it feels like\Nto have a guy in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.84,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Who would Kaito-kun be if\Nhe was part of your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.38,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Her younger brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.49,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, it does feel like that sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.70,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,but he can be really dependable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.39,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.63,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.12,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.51,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Keep doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.70,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, just act \Nlike you did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.78,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:01.30,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're here studying abroad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.46,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.73,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.56,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.46,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,A year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.55,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.90,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I shouldn't have said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.53,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.76,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.59,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.88,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.82,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lousy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:44.78,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.63,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.35,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.78,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.06,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.02,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Kai's house, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.88,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:18.76,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.15,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:25.25,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I get uneasy just watching \Nthe two of them talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.81,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like when I get like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.52,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell him you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.17,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kai still hasn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.20,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.41,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.70,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.18,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't go well, things will\Nget awkward between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.20,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We're all making a movie together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.98,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I won't \Nbe able to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.37,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'd make Kaito-kun uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.13,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.01,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to keep feeling\Nuneasy and not do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.93,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in love so you can't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.22,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You just wouldn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.07,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.03,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.10,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.45,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.60,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.73,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.01,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.49,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to have fun filming \Nthat movie over summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make the movie, and \Nshow it at the school fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:41.09,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll just keep being \Nthe usual Kanna Tanigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.59,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:48.09,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.22,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:54.98,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I had no way of knowing what \Nwas going on back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.19,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.57,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.02,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Kitahara's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.00,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I had no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:09.68,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, only one thing filled my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:14.21,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that Senpai was \Neventually going to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.59,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.55,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:26.14,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.51,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,My arms won't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.46,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A lifeform reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.23,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,And you should have just come \Nin through the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.39,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.63,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:42.94,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa was here toda—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.16,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,She likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.79,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.54,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,...likes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.26,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:43.09,Natsu-Next-Ep-Title,Kaito/Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NSenpai has a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:35.18,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.25,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:37.95,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Very stimulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:39.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, very alluring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:42.64,Natsu-Main,Kaito/Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
